<big>today && yesterday has been great, so i decided i would update.i was with bre && sara, i miss hanging out together <3 well yesterday bre came over around 5, sara got here around 6. we sat in my room and listened to music and played ddr and stuff. then around 2 we snuck out planning on going to brandons. BUT were stupid enough to go when he lives all the way of fraser. so yeah we never did make it all the way there, considering it was freezing and raining on top of it. well yeah we got back home around five in the morning. today we woke up and had breakfast. we playing ddr and got ready. then around six we went to bay lanes with brandon,ben,and brett. that wasn't that fun, because of the fucking workers there. and we had to wait in to gameroom until 9:30 for open bowling, yeah it was gay. but we played ddr and this jet-skii game, lmao me on bre's lap and sara on brandon's.but yeah we all bowled on two lanes. well bretts mom brought me home and now i'm sitting here.

i'll leave you with that.
